entry.title: Big Buck Bunny
entry.summary: A large and lovable rabbit deals with three tiny bullies, led by a flying squirrel, who are determined to squelch his happiness.

entry.title: Elephants Dream
entry.summary: Friends Proog and Emo journey inside the folds of a seemingly infinite Machine, exploring the dark and twisted complex of wires, gears, and cogs, until a moment of conflict negates all their assumptions.

entry.title: Sintel
entry.summary: A lonely young woman, Sintel, helps and befriends a dragon, whom she calls Scales. But when he is kidnapped by an adult dragon, Sintel decides to embark on a dangerous quest to find her lost friend Scales.
